- "Number of alerts" indicates the frequency of issues or problems detected;
- "Number of maintenance tasks" reflects the building's maintenance history and upkeep.

- 'active energy efficiency' refers to buildings that have an active energy efficiency rating;
- 'temperature sensors whispering the tales of warmth and cold' refers to the sensor readings of temperature;
- 'the average temperature these sensors are telling us' refers to the average temperature readings from the sensors.

