- The `sensor_data` table contains temperature and humidity readings from sensors;
- The `sensors` table maps sensors to buildings;
- The `buildings` table contains information about the buildings.

sql:
SELECT DISTINCT b.building_name
FROM buildings b
JOIN environmental_reports er ON b.building_id = er.building_id;

